  <h1><span class="ja">GSC Fukushima Hubとは</span><span class="en">About GSC Fukushima Hub</span></h1>
  <div class="ja">
    <p>Global Shapers Community Fukushima Hubは，World Economic Forumが設立した若者リーダーネットワークGlobal Shapers Communityの福島拠点である．地域と世界をつなぐ実装を通じて，福島から学び，福島に還すことを目的とする．</p><p>活動の中心は，Fukushima Study Tour，地域パートナーとの共同プロジェクト，対話と学習の場の設計である．</p>
  </div>
  <div class="en">
    <p>Global Shapers Community Fukushima Hub is the Fukushima-based hub within the Global Shapers Community, a network of young leaders founded by the World Economic Forum. Our work connects local reality with global perspectives, learning from Fukushima and giving back through action.</p><p>Core activities include the Fukushima Study Tour, collaborative projects with local partners, and spaces for dialogue and learning.</p>
  </div>
